author: Freya McClements
title: Coronavirus: Northern Ireland records 10 further deaths
description: Public Health Agency confirms eighty-five new cases bringing total to 1,967
content:
Ten more people with coronavirus have died in Northern Ireland in the last 24 hours, according to the latest figures from the Public Health Agency (PHA).
It brings the total number of patients with the virus who have died in the Norths hospitals to 134.
